{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel1 \b \fs32 1. Overview\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This package is built specifically for {\b Fedora Workstation}, which ships with the GNOME desktop. It installs and configures {\b Tiling Shell}, a GNOME Shell extension that brings Windows 11-style window management to Linux.\par}
