{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel2 \b \fs28 Custom layouts (Fancy Zones)\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 1.\tx360\tab Open Tiling Shell settings \u8594 ? {\b Layouts}\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 2.\tx360\tab Create or import custom tile grids\par}
